title: Prem Das and Murugi - Journey of the Drums Audiostrobe CD [FLAC]
description:
Audiostrobe CD for those of you with Audiostrobe compatible Mind Machines.

Prem Das and Murugi, two master drummers, present an extraordinary collaboration of rhythm and power. The steady Water drum of Prem Das provides the trance ground while Muruga's Nada Drum dances, soars, circles and hovers, always singing joyfully. This music plays with the elememental spirits of life and light, and will appeal to the urban primitive in us all.
